{
    "json_version": 0x2,
    "name": "EVENT_MESSAGE_QC04_JUR_770.ebm",
    "nb_messages": 0x1d,
    "messages": [
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xc4,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "Whew, w-we did it..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x4,
            "name_id": 0x4,
            "extra_id": 0xda,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Ayesha, I'm sorry I got you involved in this."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xc5,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "No, it's fine. I think it was inevitable, under the circumstances."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xc6,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "It's just that, I feel kinda bad for the wolf..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x4,
            "name_id": 0x4,
            "extra_id": 0xdc,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "This was his only path in life.<CR>There's no need for sympathy."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x4,
            "name_id": 0x4,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "Now, what should we do with him? Normally, I'd take the fur to sell it, but..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15a,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x4,
            "name_id": 0x4,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "What's wrong, Ayesha?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "Umm, can you leave this wolf to me...?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "This should do it. I think the wolf can rest in peace now."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x4,
            "name_id": 0x4,
            "extra_id": 0xda,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "No grave marker or anything...<CR>It's a bit lonely for a grave."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x4,
            "name_id": 0x4,
            "extra_id": 0xdb,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "But anyone out for his fur won't know that he rests here."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x4,
            "name_id": 0x4,
            "extra_id": 0xdc,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "msg_string": "Still, this is my first experience with making a grave for my prey."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x4,
            "name_id": 0x4,
            "extra_id": 0x15a,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "msg_string": "It's not the kind of idea a huntsman<CR>would have, but this could be good,<CR>as is."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xe,
            "msg_string": "Juris, you told me to not sympathize with him, but..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xc4,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0xf,
            "msg_string": "My heart aches whenever I think about this wolf's feelings."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x4,
            "name_id": 0x4,
            "extra_id": 0x15b,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x10,
            "msg_string": "In this land, with limited resources, it's hard for humans and beasts to get along."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x4,
            "name_id": 0x4,
            "extra_id": 0x15c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x11,
            "msg_string": "Sympathizing every time would cause us to starve."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xc6,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x12,
            "msg_string": "Is that...how it works?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x4,
            "name_id": 0x4,
            "extra_id": 0x8,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x13,
            "msg_string": "Still, he was able to die as one who hunts, not as one who is hunted."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x4,
            "name_id": 0x4,
            "extra_id": 0x9,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x14,
            "msg_string": "He may not agree or be satisfied... However..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x4,
            "name_id": 0x4,
            "extra_id": 0xc,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x15,
            "msg_string": "Let's choose to believe that, at the very least, he had no regrets."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x193,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x16,
            "msg_string": "You're right... Or I guess I have no choice but to think of it like that."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x4,
            "name_id": 0x4,
            "extra_id": 0x12,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x17,
            "msg_string": "That's it. Now, let's go back to town and tell Kyle."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x18,
            "msg_string": "Yeah. I'm sure he's worried about us, too."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x4,
            "name_id": 0x4,
            "extra_id": 0x9,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x19,
            "msg_string": "I wonder... Knowing him, he might've forgotten all about the wolf..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x4,
            "name_id": 0x4,
            "extra_id": 0x9,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1a,
            "msg_string": "Well, telling that chatterbox will quickly get the word out that the wolf was exterminated."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1b,
            "msg_string": "Most likely. We need to reassure everyone in town!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x1c,
            "msg_string": "(I have mixed feelings, but...I guess this was for the best...)"
        }
    ]
}